-- MBIA shares jump after capital infusion news
-- 
-- Mon Dec 10, 2007 11:15am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/12/10/us-markets-stocks-mbia-idUSN1041365320071210

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Shares of MBIA Inc ( MBI.N ) jumped more than 20 percent to $36.36 on Monday as the stock resumed trading following news that the mortgage insurer had received a commitment for a $1 billion capital infusion.  

 (Reporting by  Ellis Mnyandu ; Editing by  James Dalgleish )